<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>404 - Halaman Tidak Ditemukan</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #222528, #000000);
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      perspective: 1000px;
    }

    .container {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 50px 40px; 
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 10px 10px 25px #cfd4da, -10px -10px 25px #ffffff;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out, tilt 5s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      transform: rotateX(8deg) rotateY(0deg);
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 100px;
      color: #5a6f8c;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 12px rgba(90, 111, 140, 0.2);
      transform: translateZ(20px);
    }

    p {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      color: #7c8a9f;
      transform: translateZ(10px);
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: #4b6cb7;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(75, 108, 183, 0.3);
      transform: translateZ(30px);
    }

    a:hover {
      background-color: #3957a5;
      transform: scale(1.06) translateZ(40px);
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scale(0.8);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1);
      }
    }

    @keyframes tilt {
      0% {
        transform: rotateX(8deg) rotateY(-3deg);
      }
      100% {
        transform: rotateX(8deg) rotateY(3deg);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>Ups! Halaman yang kamu cari tidak ditemukan.</p>
    <a href="/">Kembali ke Beranda</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
